  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a clay tandoor pot over medium heat for tadka.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add chopped peanut brittle and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add tomato paste and curry powder, stir well and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add fish and coconut milk, stir to combine.",
    "Add lime juice and brown sugar, stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer covered for 20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve over rice or with roti.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Store leftovers in the refrigerator for up to 3 days."
  ],
